Data Deletion / Account Deletion

You can request deletion of your Flowy account and personal data at any time by contacting andreaballarin94@gmail.com.
When we receive a verified deletion request, we will delete or anonymize your personal data, including account information such as email, name, and profile photo, and habit data associated with your account, unless we are required to keep certain information for legal, security, accounting, or fraud-prevention purposes.
Some information may remain in backups for a limited period of time before being automatically removed.
After deletion, your account access will be disabled and your stored data will no longer be available in the app.
